SCHEMA IS THE TRANSLATOR FOR DDL PROGRAMS.
-----------------
COMMAND STRING

	.R SCHEMA
	*SCHFIL=DDLFIL

THE OUTPUT EXTENSION IS ALWAYS FORCED TO .SCH.
THE DEFAULT INPUT EXTENSION IF .DDL.
IF ABSENT, THE OUTPUT FILENAME DEFAULTS TO THE INPUT FILE NAME.

/CREATE CONTROLS WHETHER THE .DBS FILES ARE (RE)CREATED.
	/CREATE SAYS RECREATE
	/NOCREATE SAYS DO NOT CREATE
	NO-SWITCH SAYS CREATE, BUT DO NOT SUPERCEDE

[END SCHEMA.HLP]
